            <article><span>01</span><div><h3>Sewer camera inspections</h3><p>Non-invasive assessment to locate and evaluate root intrusion severity. We pinpoint exactly where roots have entered and how extensive the damage is.</p></div></article>
            <article><span>02</span><div><h3>Professional root removal</h3><p>Using <a href="../../../drain-and-sewer-services/hydro-jetting/">hydro jetting</a> and mechanical augers, we clear root blockages safely and thoroughly without damaging the surrounding pipe.</p></div></article>
            <article><span>03</span><div><h3>Root treatment application</h3><p>Professional-grade root treatment kills invasive roots effectively and prevents regrowth, extending the time between cleanings.</p></div></article>
            <article><span>04</span><div><h3>Trenchless repair</h3><p>Pipe lining and pipe bursting minimize landscaping disruption. A new pipe is created inside the old one or pulled through to replace it — without digging up your yard.</p></div></article>
